{"tid":1397806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Big 4員工自發籲8.5罷工 核數師齊聲：Stand for HK！","createTime":"2019-08-02T15:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:21:47.000Z","uid":212249,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"06c3a865a7a2b38b86c335b7d240e7d8bf9b8e84","tid":1397806,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190802/large/1564744042_e83d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190802%2Flarge%2F1564744042_e83d.png&h=068b55e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金融界紛發聲響應8月5日罷工行動，四大會計師行員工，分別自製宣傳海報。羅兵咸永道（PwC）、畢馬威（KPMG）、安永（EY）海報明言「Stand for HK」。德勤（Dtt）則指，「Green dot or black cops」。<br />\n<br />\nPwC海報又呼籲同事當天善用公司WeFlex政策。WeFlex為PwC的靈活工作安排政策，讓員工能夠每天根據實際情況，靈活地選擇工作時間、地點和方式。至於安永製作的文宣，更呼籲同事為香港，參與下周一的遊行。<br />\n會計界網絡博客阿樹表示，自己周一亦會參與罷工，至於其現仍於Big 4工作的前同事亦會響應。他表示，除Big 4外，2nd-tier會計師行亦有製作文宣，設計海報呼籲同業罷工，暫時未聽過有會計師行向擬請假同事施壓。<br />\n<br />\n本報就此向四大會計師行查詢，周一會否有特別安排，以及會否對罷工員工秋後算帳，安永表示未有回應。至於德勤、畢馬威、羅兵咸永道暫未回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190802/59890477?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3rKz94kN-0wOE6KwNKdMjzP8UIqx7YRd2MYJdXF5xoiae0HCV3m6oRrCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190802%2F59890477%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3rKz94kN-0wOE6KwNKdMjzP8UIqx7YRd2MYJdXF5xoiae0HCV3m6oRrCQ&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzVyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=b2d039e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190802%2F59890477%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3rKz94kN-0wOE6KwNKdMjzP8UIqx7YRd2MYJdXF5xoiae0HCV3m6oRrCQ&h=473534a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190802/59890477?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3rKz94kN-0wOE6KwNKdMjzP8UIqx7YRd2MYJdXF5xoiae0HCV3m6oRrCQ</a>"},{"pid":"b503b5791b3af58d94e3119d2334779a5f9d400e","tid":1397806,"uid":14958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:20:27.000Z","msg":"我做big4<br />\n我會擺工"},{"pid":"22a767430066b8018af1650439283e5c770e0533","tid":1397806,"uid":266635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}